data.description: ATTN: 15K ADJUSTMENT & NOW -10K- CONCESSION TOWARD RATE BUY DOWN or USE AS YOU CHOOSE thru 12/31! Open concept home w/ unique features is perfect for starting out, downsizing, or as rental w/ room for your own touches. Refreshed w/ new paint inside & out, featuring a modern IKEA inspired kitchen w/ white & stainless steel cabinetry, drawers & countertops, pantry, Koda smart light system w/ remotes. Equipped w/ newer mini-splits for cooling & heating needs. Enjoy the custom fireplace on cooler nights. Other updates & newer items in last 8 yrs include windows w/ UV film for energy conservation, laminate floors, part metal roof, water heater, stove, light fixtures, RV hookup & Ryobi garage door opener w/ all the bells & whistles. Back courtyard patio & enough yard to make your private oasis!
